::Savanna::

She looked about for others who had made it.  "Phobia," she whipsered.
"a trap. shortly after we got here, the preds came. He must have set 
us up."
She growled a loud and low growl.  She was mad and wanted to hear it 
from the bot himself before ripping out his spark with her own claws.
